Scope: Enhance ConsoleLoggerAdapter with structured per-stage logging: logStageStart and logStageEnd emit JSON lines with stage name, event type (start/end), duration in milliseconds (via ClockPort), and token counts. logFailedModels emits model identifier, error code, and error message truncated to ≤200 characters. Update the DI container to wire the enhanced logger and ClockPort to all components. This is a cross-phase modification of console-logger-adapter.ts (originally created Task 04) and container.ts (Task 05) to add production observability.
